# --- [ Whitelisting of Molecules in the Bloodstream ] ---

* Whitelisting of Molecules in the Bloodstream

By applying the concept of whitelisting it could be possible to create a filter within the bloodstream similar to those used by anti-virus software. The filter would protect vital organs from lethal doses of any one molecule.

